    [ctns_front]
Slope $$m = \frac{ \Delta y }{ \Delta x}$$ <br/>
For Decreasing Values of $$y$$
    [/ctns_front]

    [ctns_back style='width:80%;font-size:90%;']
The slope $$m$$ is Negative for increasing values of $$x$$
but decreasing values of $$y$$,

$|m = \frac{ \Delta y }{ \Delta x} \lt 0|$
    [/ctns_back]
    
    [ctns_backspeak]
The slope m is Negative for increasing values of x
and decreasing values of y.
    [/ctns_backspeak]
    

[/ctns_make]
